node.text: It was an outstanding weekend at the #MonacoGP with the launch of the new #TAGHeuerMonaco Titan Special Edition and the victory of @redbullracing driver @maxverstappen1. Special thanks to @car_vintage, @watchanish, @supercarblondie and @tedgushue for joining us on the French Riviera.

node.text: Fresh off of his own race, @tagheuerporschefe driver @andre_lotterer takes a ride through the iconic streets of Monaco and shares with us what he thinks makes the #MonacoGP so special.
